Date: 0/0/1956
Source: Wool Away!
Author: BOWEN
Vol / Page: 158
Edition:
Quote: `WOOL AWAY.' When the fleece has not been cleared off the board by the `fleeco' and is in the shearer's way, a shearer will make this call. So may I also, having come to the end of the textbook on shearing, say to all readers WOOL AWAY!
